{"tid":238149,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"PRIUS S，點揸最慳油？","createTime":"2017-05-11T00:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T12:58:17.000Z","uid":45223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76a64e72618b91cbd8a8cca8fcdd5dcbcd0e5a8f","tid":238149,"uid":45223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T00:01:39.000Z","msg":"早前咨詢過巴絲對Prius C嘅意見之後<br />\n<br />\n就膽粗粗去左試車<br />\n<br />\n最後因爲後座舒適度大啲 所以選擇左Prius S<br />\n<br />\n揸左三日，大部分時間用ECO mode<br />\n<br />\n上落斜會轉下B波儲電<br />\n<br />\n但油耗都係由一開始21km/L跌到16km/L <br />\n<br />\n想問下巴絲們，點揸先最慳油??<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知無可能做到官方數字27km/L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實hybrid車控制油門係咪有技巧？<br />\n<br />\n例如起動架車要好細腳、適當轉EV mode 行咁？"},{"pid":"e65546a679bfcd5b2191a574d3e39494acd9f307","tid":238149,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T00:06:19.000Z","msg":"我想問試車俾你試幾耐<br />\n試完唔買會唔會俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efffef1ccf41ce2ddb3d4e52db0a3ccfc187205","tid":238149,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T00:26:44.000Z","msg":"泊車場唔揸最慳油<br />\n<br />\n係日本揸Prius 既經驗<br />\n起步唔好比油由佢溜順左先慢慢印油門<br />\n唔好比佢上到pwr 就最慳<br />\n不過係支燈起步上到50 都講緊五六秒<br />\n香港比人砵爆"},{"pid":"2097221dd0e3c935410fac590771a54a8532f8ec","tid":238149,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T00:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泊車場唔揸最慳油<br />\n<br />\n係日本揸Prius 既經驗<br />\n起步唔好比油由佢溜順左先慢慢印油門<br />\n唔好比佢上到pwr 就最慳<br />\n不過係支燈起步上到50 都講緊五六秒<br />\n香港比人砵爆</blockquote><br />\n定eco<br />\npwr 好似已經係紅<br />\n如果係ev - eco - pwr<br />\n就唔好比佢過eco<br />\n揸新Prius 試過1X公里 overall 9X分"},{"pid":"541efbe969f4aefada617d142b9c336314ccb64f","tid":238149,"uid":45223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問試車俾你試幾耐<br />\n試完唔買會唔會俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你咩人啦"},{"pid":"901c7e61d334c1176abea623edefe6778e335433","tid":238149,"uid":45223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泊車場唔揸最慳油<br />\n<br />\n係日本揸Prius 既經驗<br />\n起步唔好比油由佢溜順左先慢慢印油門<br />\n唔好比佢上到pwr 就最慳<br />\n不過係支燈起步上到50 都講緊五六秒<br />\n香港比人砵爆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲見佢條bar係咁上 上到pwr以為最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfc85ab9814c21bfcf8cf03da7a595cc19e74fb","tid":238149,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>泊車場唔揸最慳油<br />\n<br />\n係日本揸Prius 既經驗<br />\n起步唔好比油由佢溜順左先慢慢印油門<br />\n唔好比佢上到pwr 就最慳<br />\n不過係支燈起步上到50 都講緊五六秒<br />\n香港比人砵爆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲見佢條bar係咁上 上到pwr以為最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽引擎聲都知唔係啦下嘛...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cabd8b32b1ffd5f1cbbdf64244d21a68d55916","tid":238149,"uid":9766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:04:58.000Z","msg":"Prius舊電最好唔好大差大放，依個係uber司機教落，如果唔係好快要換電。"},{"pid":"d28298e5982a9e6fb0520ea806d54ed729c1a081","tid":238149,"uid":45223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Prius舊電最好唔好大差大放，依個係uber司機教落，如果唔係好快要換電。</blockquote><br />\n點先做到唔大差大放<br />\n認真救教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e63ec0a17175a5d9512f991a348f7ec37e89d8","tid":238149,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Prius舊電最好唔好大差大放，依個係uber司機教落，如果唔係好快要換電。</blockquote><br />\n點先做到唔大差大放<br />\n認真救教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你識唔識得睇佢個indicator點先為之差電？<br />\n差電佢都有唔同格數<br />\n你揸既時候留意下點做先可以令到佢差既時候唔會大差大放<br />\n簡單講就比人唔好比大油，brake 唔好大brake（其實揸乜車都係）<br />\n不過幅度既野好難文字講"},{"pid":"40dab6ce3ca03bed7335413434a255f88b2e0ed4","tid":238149,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"同埋佢個km/l 都係估數<br />\n你大腳篤一篤個數就彈，收一收油溜又變<br />\n根本做唔到準<br />\n下下望住個數字黎揸，倒不如專心路面情況到入油果陣先計數"},{"pid":"f0c108f17776e0ba4bb79c614667aeed02292293","tid":238149,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"買柴油車咪唔使咁煩囉"},{"pid":"eba883362017bfe48d1fa21a3c7b93cae0973eab","tid":238149,"uid":45223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋佢個km/l 都係估數<br />\n你大腳篤一篤個數就彈，收一收油溜又變<br />\n根本做唔到準<br />\n下下望住個數字黎揸，倒不如專心路面情況到入油果陣先計數</blockquote><br />\n巴打說話啱聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cc090641eb9f82e8769e6ed47f8041663b9abf","tid":238149,"uid":45223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40ySsbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40ySsbt.jpg&h=fff39acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊條bar有時會去到pwr <br />\n尤其落左B波上斜 好多時都會pwr<br />\n但上斜係咪用返D波仲好呢？"},{"pid":"20b2eb6775ea1fb337835b3af87c37e0db750dff","tid":238149,"uid":71524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"你唔好下下地板油咁去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一放break，會有少少動力行既，之後先俾油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋停車等紅綠燈/塞車之類既都唔好落n波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣會放曬大電d電<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正，屋企人揸過prius一排<br />\n<br />\n同埋你個部全新定二手呀？<br />\n二手既你睇下有冇損耗品未換，都有少少影響"},{"pid":"8b290903c331827f21c020ae85fe78e63a44398c","tid":238149,"uid":64483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40ySsbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40ySsbt.jpg&h=fff39acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊條bar有時會去到pwr <br />\n尤其落左B波上斜 好多時都會pwr<br />\n但上斜係咪用返D波仲好呢？</blockquote><br />\n全程行D已經得<br />\n其實條bar間接反映你踩幾大油 上斜要去到pwr係正常既 普通行街keep住pwr條線以下就好慳"},{"pid":"b903235f6fb587ca2fda6d37fb950e595480dae1","tid":238149,"uid":103534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"我揸Prius 1800cc<br />\n<br />\n起步直踩上power <br />\n到左適當速度，50 or above 就縮腳，再印住行，盡量keep住行電或者混能mode<br />\n<br />\n上大斜照比爆油上，落斜唔比油，印住落或者b 波<br />\n<br />\n如果前面紅燈就會唔比油，等自己sir<br />\n<br />\n要訣<br />\n<br />\n盡量比車滑行<br />\n到左適當速度，要完全縮腳再印翻<br />\n<br />\n伸利: 長期21.1km/l<br />\n最高見22km/l<br />\n入中石油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e252aad7a1c155d1b2b5731cd33cc83c3053321c","tid":238149,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40ySsbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40ySsbt.jpg&h=fff39acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊條bar有時會去到pwr <br />\n尤其落左B波上斜 好多時都會pwr<br />\n但上斜係咪用返D波仲好呢？</blockquote><br />\n除左落斜會用b波，平時千期咪長開，小心拖爆舊電。。"},{"pid":"c08add34784d4cc3d4bcb7f6dfca52e5e29bb642","tid":238149,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早前咨詢過巴絲對Prius C嘅意見之後<br />\n<br />\n就膽粗粗去左試車<br />\n<br />\n最後因爲後座舒適度大啲 所以選擇左Prius S<br />\n<br />\n揸左三日，大部分時間用ECO mode<br />\n<br />\n上落斜會轉下B波儲電<br />\n<br />\n但油耗都係由一開始21km/L跌到16km/L <br />\n<br />\n想問下巴絲們，點揸先最慳油??<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知無可能做到官方數字27km/L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實hybrid車控制油門係咪有技巧？<br />\n<br />\n例如起動架車要好細腳、適當轉EV mode 行咁？</blockquote><br />\n上斜用乜鬼B 波&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c4bd946ed1815693f0482eb446bf23a50b2e2c95","tid":238149,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"助跑上斜同唔好半路縮油應該可以再慳啲"}]}